data.description: Looking for new construction but don't want to wait on building? This 1400+ sq ft, gorgeous ranch on a basement is ready for you. Board and batten accent the entryway as you come in from the covered front porch. With it's split floor plan you'll find two bedrooms and a full bath at the front of the house. Laundry is conveniently located near the garage entrance and features custom wood shelving for extra organized space. Hallway opens to the living room with tray ceiling and recessed lighting. Kitchen features upgraded 40" white kitchen cabinets with soft close doors & drawers. Large island provides tons of storage and extra seating space and the dining room rounds out the open floor plan. The master suite is tucked off the living room and features a double vanity with soft close doors, custom shelving and walk in shower.  Kitchen and dining room have upgraded lighting. Craftsman doors, LVP flooring, black hardware and fixtures throughout. Even the carpet padding was upgraded! The basement is huge and plumbed for a bath as well - the potential for extra square footage here is amazing! Under 1 year builder warranty til March 2024. You can't build this house with the upgrades for this price currently!
